{
  "stem": "10162.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would hear this at home, the talk between my parents and their friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually, in Hungary, all this happened much faster.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything was very condensed in time compared to what happened in-- in Poland and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- we really didn't feel anti-Semitism until '43.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then in '44, suddenly, it just-- the world fell apart you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to-- well, even before we had to wear the yellow star, suddenly, there were stores having a sign out saying [HUNGARIAN], which means Hungarian store or Hungarian business, which really meant that Jews are not welcome, this is a Hungarian store.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So suddenly there was-- were Hungarians and Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there we were, Hungarian Jews who-- who lived in Hungary probably longer than-- than most people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Hungary is-- Hungarians are a very mixed race.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- there are so many minorities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe they came to [INAUDIBLE], they came from Germany a generation or two ago, or-- or Slovaks, or Serbians, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were there for as long as we could go back-- great-grandfather's grandfathers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So how could anybody tell us that we are not Hungarians?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly, they say Hungarian store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this store might have been a toy store where we were going ever since I remembered and they-- they greeted my-- my mother very-- very politely.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we couldn't go in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was just all around us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my mother had two cousins, girls, who were about the same ages she was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were also living in Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they also got married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So her two cousins were her best friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And their husbands were best friends with my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were also always some friends coming in from-- you know, from other families.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this-- the three girls were very close.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And actually, my mother cousin's son, who was also an only child and also about the same age as I am, was my best friend.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were brought up together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father had a sister, an older sister, who lived in Debrecen who we were friendly like family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she was older than my mother and not quite-- it wasn't-- it wasn't real friendship, just family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I only had one grandmother living in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my grandfather, who I remember-- he must have been maybe-- I must have been maybe seven when he died.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my grandmother lived in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went very often back and forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your mother's mother?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's mother, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father's parents died when I was maybe a year old or earlier.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't remember them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I just-- I-- my mother went fairly regularly because she had a younger brother in France.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she would go visit him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she went once or twice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know they went to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then she used to go to-- to Italy on a tour to Abbazia, it was called.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now I think it's Opatija.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's part of whatever that is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's not Yugoslavia anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- I don't know if it's Serbia or Croatia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the only time I went with my mother was to Italy, to this Abbazia once.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I must have been six.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I have very, very little recollection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were discussions, because this was the discussion of the day among Jews altogether.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody came and loved to hear my father's opinion.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
